{"id":"a3ea0b6b-d305-462d-98bb-d742ef9fe823","name":"Saint Seiya Myth Cloth Ex Action Figure Limnades Casa 18cm (Sealed box)","slug":"saint-seiya-myth-cloth-ex-action-figurea","description":"<p><strong>Saint Seiya Myth Cloth </strong><b>Ex </b>Action Figure of <b>Limnades Casa</b>, size approx.18cm. <strong>Official product</strong> by <strong>Tamashii Nations</strong>.</p>\n<p>The last of the Marina Generals, <strong>Limnades Casa</strong>, joins <strong>Saint Cloth Myth EX</strong>! Featuring new sculpting, it allows you to post <strong>Limnades Casa</strong> in his distinctive fighting pose!</p>\n<p><strong>Limnades Casa</strong> is a Marina General capable of assuming the guise of his opponents' loved ones and proves to be a serious obstacle for many <strong>Bronze Saints.</strong></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\">Content:</span></strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Main body</li>\n<li>Three left and four right optional hands</li>\n<li>Surplice set</li>\n<li>Object mode frame</li>\n<li>Four optional expression parts</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Box C10 condition (box are checked before sending).<br /><br />This product is not a toy or product for children. It is a collectors item intended for adults only.</p>","metaTitle":null,"metaDescription":null,"model":null,"releaseDate":null,"image":null,"condition":null,"edition":null,"rarity":null,"features":null,"specifications":null,"createdAt":"2025-04-06T11:28:32.229Z","updatedAt":"2025-04-06T11:28:32.229Z","barcode":"4573102629814","deletedAt":null,"source":"heo","hasFakeBarcode":false,"duplicateId":null,"brandId":"3a466736-f80f-4cbd-a1a0-d34efc302efd","franchiseId":null,"seriesId":null,"lineId":null,"categories":[{"productId":"a3ea0b6b-d305-462d-98bb-d742ef9fe823","categoryId":"c6ea4121-907d-426e-8774-80e229d31d4c","category":{"id":"c6ea4121-907d-426e-8774-80e229d31d4c","name":"Collectibles","slug":"collectibles","description":"Collectible items","image":null,"parentId":null,"createdAt":"2025-03-27T23:28:51.587Z","